Demographic Trends





(Alleged) Consequences of Diversity


Small groups: from what you’ve been hearing in the news, in discussions with friends/family, etc., what are some possible reasons that policymakers and ordinary citizens would be concerned about immigration?


Some Outcomes from the Literature
  • Greater prejudice against minorities
  • Growing support for far-right parties / candidates
  • More crime
  • Civil violence
  • Slower economic growth
  • Worse public goods provision
  • Reduced support for social services / “welfare chauvinism”
  • Erosion of social norms, trust, cooperation
